    "authors": "YOUR_NAME",
    "name": "AI Business Insights & Alert System (Google Sheets → Gmail)",
    "description": "This workflow is an AI-powered business monitoring and alert system built using n8n.\n\nIt automatically fetches daily business data from Google Sheets, analyzes it using an AI agent, and sends actionable insights via email.\n\nKey Features:\n- AI-generated business insights and trends\n- Revenue drop detection using percentage-based logic\n- Low lead detection for early pipeline issues\n- Smart alert system with priority-based decision flow\n- Automated email reports via Gmail\n\nHow it works:\n1. Fetches daily data (Sales, Leads, Revenue) from Google Sheets\n2. Formats and processes data for analysis\n3. Uses AI to generate insights, trends, and recommendations\n4. Detects anomalies (revenue drops, low leads)\n5. Sends alerts or daily reports via Gmail\n\nUse Cases:\n- Small business performance monitoring\n- Startup growth tracking\n- Sales and marketing analytics\n- Daily automated reporting without dashboards\n\nThis workflow helps businesses move from passive reporting to proactive decision-making.",
